 When api is moved to prod envo than it is called web service 
 all web-services are API but not all Api are WEBSERVICES 
 
 It is an open source library hence free and are used for testing and validating REST api 
 it is capable of validating HTTP RESPONSE FROM THE SERVER. very rich in syntax and ready made assertions
 rest assured is easy and straightforward 
 response is given in json or xml format and easy to parse and validate 
 it can be easiy integrated with other java libraries like testng 
